      "description": "## What's New\n\n- **Require modifier key** - Only show preview when holding a modifier key (⌘ on Mac, Ctrl on Windows/Linux). Enabled by default.\n- **Configurable modifier key** - Choose between Command, Control, Alt, or Shift\n- **Close on key release** - Option to keep preview open until mouse leave or ESC\n\n## Installation\n\nDownload `main.js`, `manifest.json`, and `styles.css` and place them in your vault's `.obsidian/plugins/url-preview/` directory.",
